##Auto-Resolve Existing Events with Alert/Incident Keys
Selecting the last option in your email management rules -- `}<strong parentName="p">{`create and resolve incidents based on custom rules`}</strong>{` -- allows you to automatically resolve incidents from email integrations by parsing message content.`}</p>
    <p>{`Email management uses a set of rules that is applied to any incoming email. Each rule has three components:`}</p>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">{`A `}<strong parentName="li">{`condition`}</strong>{` that tells PagerDuty if the email should create an event`}</li>
      <li parentName="ol">{`A `}<strong parentName="li">{`condition`}</strong>{` that tells PagerDuty if the email should resolve an event`}</li>
      <li parentName="ol">{`An `}<strong parentName="li">{`alert`}</strong>{` or `}<strong parentName="li">{`incident key`}</strong>{` that tells PagerDuty how to match one email with another email.
`}{`[block:image]`}{`
